"'''Puzzle Peace'''" is a [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] that was first published in [[Star Wars Tales 13|''Star Wars Tales'' 13]] and was collected in ''[[Star Wars Tales Volume 4]]''.

==Plot summary==
On [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], [[Mace Windu/Legends|Mace Windu]] explains to [[Yoda/Legends|Yoda]] how his talks with the [[Er'stacian]]s went...

Windu arrived on [[Er'stacia]] to find a war in progress between rival clans. After negotiating a cease-fire with the help of his force abilities, Windu discovered the clans are fighting over ownership of a large statue known as the [[Venerable One]]. A warrior accidentally shot at Windu with his [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]], desecrating the statue, and he was torn apart by his fellow Er'Stacians.

Seeing that he cannot end the conflict by negotiation, Windu carved up the statue into a thousand pieces, leaving the Er'Stacians with something other than war to consider.

